message.content:
A small kitchen with black lower and upper cabinets lines one corner, topped by a marble‐colored countertop. A sink is set into the left portion of the counter below a wooden‐framed window. Moving right along the counter, a stove with a small pot sits near a wooden range hood overhead. Next to the stove are an orange mug, a box featuring a cartoon face, a jar of fruit spread, a stack of white dishes, a box labeled “Rice Bubbles,” another red box with similar graphics, a package of strawberry gelatin dessert, and a cylindrical container of salt. Under and above this counter are closed black cabinets with matching handles. A tall black cabinet stands beside a white refrigerator, which marks the transition from the kitchen to the dining area.

In the dining area, a rectangular wooden table occupies the center, surrounded by four white upholstered chairs. On the table, a white rectangular bowl containing several round fruits also cradles a large water bottle. A black rectangular carton rests nearby, along with a clear pitcher and a single stemmed glass. A white door is set in the wall behind the table, and a round ceiling light fixture hangs above. The floor throughout is a parquet wood pattern, and the walls are painted white.
